raw: Asian giant hornet workers can grow to 1.5 inches in length and are     similar in size to other wasps that occur in Pennsylvania and may be confused with     Asian giant hornets. Asian giant hornets are strikingly colored, with yellow heads, a     black thorax, and yellow and black or brown striped abdomens.
